#99f;\" |Not Free\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |[[Muhammadu Buhari]]\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 1985\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |7\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |5\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |Not Free\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |&nbsp;Muhammadu&nbsp;Buhari&nbsp;\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 1986\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |7\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |5\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |Not Free\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |[[Ibrahim Babangida]]\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 1987\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |6\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |5\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |Not Free\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |Ibrahim Babangida\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 1988\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |5\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |5\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Partly Free\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Ibrahim Babangida\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 1989\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |6\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |5\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |Not Free\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |Ibrahim Babangida\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 1990\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |5\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |5\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Partly Free\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Ibrahim Babangida\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 1991\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |5\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Partly Free\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Ibrahim Babangida\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 1992\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |5\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Partly Free\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Ibrahim Babangida\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 1993\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |7\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |5\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |Not Free\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |Ibrahim Babangida\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 1994\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |7\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |6\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |Not Free\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |[[Sani Abacha]]\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 1995\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |7\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |7\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |Not Free\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |Sani Abacha\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 1996\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |7\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |6\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |Not Free\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |Sani Abacha\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 1997\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |7\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |6\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |Not Free\n| style=\"background:#99f;\" |Sani Abacha\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 1998\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |6\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Partly Free\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Sani Abacha\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 1999\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |3\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Partly Free\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |[[Abdulsalami Abubakar]]\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 2000\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Partly Free\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |[[Olusegun Obasanjo]]\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 2001\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |5\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Partly Free\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Olusegun Obasanjo\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 2002\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |5\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Partly Free\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Olusegun Obasanjo\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 2003\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Partly Free\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Olusegun Obasanjo\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 2004\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Partly Free\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Olusegun Obasanjo\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 2005\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Partly Free\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Olusegun Obasanjo\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 2006\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Partly Free\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Olusegun Obasanjo\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 2007\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Partly Free\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Olusegun Obasanjo\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 2008\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |5\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Partly Free\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |[[Umaru Musa Yar'Adua]]\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 2009\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |5\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Partly Free\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |&nbsp;Umaru&nbsp;Musa&nbsp;Yar'Adua&nbsp;\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 2010\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Partly Free\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Umaru Musa Yar'Adua\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 2011\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Partly Free\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |[[Goodluck Jonathan]]\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 2012\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |5\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Partly Free\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Goodluck Jonathan\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 2013\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Partly Free\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Goodluck Jonathan\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 2014\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Partly Free\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Goodluck Jonathan\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 2015\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |5\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Partly Free\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Goodluck Jonathan\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 2016\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |5\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Partly Free\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |[[Muhammadu Buhari]]\n|- align=center\n| align=left | 2017\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |3\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |5\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Partly Free\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\" |Muhammadu Buhari\n|-\n|colspan=5 style=\"padding:0; border:none;\"|\n<small>'''Notes:'''\n:a.{{note|a}}Note that the \"Year\" signifies the \"Year covered\". Therefore the information for the year marked 2008 is from the report published in 2009, and so on.\n:b.{{note|b}}As of 1 January.\n:c.{{note|c}}The 1982 report covers the year 1981 and the first half of 1982, and the following 1984 report covers the second half of 1982 and the whole of 1983. In the interest of simplicity, these two aberrant \"year and a half\" reports have been split into three year-long reports through interpolation.</small>\n|}\n|}\n\n==International treaties==\nNigeria's stances on [[International human rights law|international human rights treaties]] are as follows:\n\n{| class=\"wikitable collapsible collapsed\" style=\"border:none; \"\n!Treaties\n|-\n|style=\"padding:0; border:none;\"|\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" width=100% style=\"border-collapse:collapse;\"\n|- style=\"background:#eee; font-weight:bold; text-align:center;\"\n| Treaty\n| Organization\n| Introduced\n| Signed\n| Accession, Ratification\n|- align=center\n| style=\"background:#9f9; align=left\" | [[Convention on the Prevention and Punishment of the Crime of Genocide]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://treaties.un.org/Pages/ViewDetails.aspx?src=TREATY&mtdsg_no=IV-1&chapter=4&lang=en |title=United Nations Treaty Collection: Chapter IV: Human Rights: 1. Convention on the Prevention and Punishment of the